name: Frank Micheal
description: I am an honest down to earth man with a good heart easy going easy to get along with I don’t like to play games or have drama in my life I love to laugh and enjoy everyday life is too short to waste I enjoy cooking dining out barbeques reading swimming bowling walking camping and a lot more but if you want to know more you have to ask I am very open minded and really believe that special women I have been looking for is out there I just have not found her yet.
